logout page bypass action ''logout'' but not ''loggedout=true''.</p><p><strong>Version 1.0.1 (4/16/13)</strong></p><p>Code updates.</p><p><strong>Version 1.0.0 (4/10/13)</strong></p><p>Initial release.</p></div><div\nid="extendd-license" class="group"><p>Your purchase is good for one year of auto updates with a valid license key (if provided) by this plugin. You may update your license key at any time by visiting the "My Account" page.</p></div> </section> </article><p>The post <a\nrel="nofollow" href="https://extendd.com/plugin/custom-login-stealth-login/">Custom Login Stealth Login</a> appeared first on <a\nrel="nofollow" href="https://extendd.com">Extendd</a>.</p> ";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:59:"https://extendd.com/plugin/custom-login-stealth-login/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:9:"         ";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:6:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:16:"Custom Login 2.0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:40:"https://extendd.com/plugin/custom-login/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:49:"https://extendd.com/plugin/custom-login/#comments";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Tue, 16 Apr 2013 18:50:50 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:45:"http://extendd.dev/?post_type=download&p=8070";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:337:"<p>WordPress Custom Login 2.0 is all new. You can still download the plugin for FREE in the WordPress repo, but you''ll find all extension here on Extendd.</p><p>The post <a\nrel="nofollow" href="https://extendd.com/plugin/custom-login/">Custom Login 2.0</a> appeared first on <a\nrel="nofollow" href="https://extendd.com">Extendd</a>.</p> ";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:12:"Austin Passy";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:3504:"<p><strong>Version 2.0</strong> is now 140% faster in the admin and uses a lot less resources! Join in on the <a\nhref="http://austinpassy.com/wordpress-plugins/custom-login">conversation</a> on my personal blog.</p><h4>Extensions</h4><p>Custom Login 2.0 now has many extensions to make your login page better.</p><p><strong>Currently Available:</strong></p><ul><li>Custom Login: <a\nhref="http://extendd.com/plugin/custom-login-stealth-login/" title="Custom Login Stealth Login">Stealth Login</a> &#8211; obscure your login URL.</li><li>Custom Login: <a\nhref="http://extendd.com/plugin/custom-login-page-template/" title="Custom Login Page Template">Page Template</a> &#8211; turn a WordPress page into a login form.</li><li>Custom Login: <a\nhref="http://extendd.com/plugin/wordpress-login-redirects/" title="WordPress Login Redirects">Redirects</a> &#8211; redirect users by role after logging in.</li><li><strong><a\nhref="http://extendd.com/plugin/custom-login-bundle/" title="Custom Login Bundle">The Bundle</a></strong></li></ul><p><strong>In Development/Ideas</strong></p><ul><li>User Hash Key logins (think generated guest logins with-out having to use the login form).</li><li>Email Logins for usernames.</li><li>2-step Authentication.</li><li><a\nhref="http://extendd.com/plugin/custom-login-page-template/" title="Custom Login Page Template">Custom Login page</a>.</li><li>&#8220;Super User&#8221; only access for client sites.</li><li>WordPress Login CSS style remover (for sites that see a quick flash of the default login page).</li><li>Submit button styles!</li><li>Custom Login Templates</li></ul><h4>More info</h4><p>Activate the plugin and customize your WordPress login screen. Use the built-in and easy to use settings page to do the work for you. There&#8217;s no need to understand CSS at all! Now featureing a HTML, CSS &amp; jQuery box for advanced users to up the customization!</p><ol><li>Works great for client site installs.</li><li>Read more about <a\nhref="http://wp.me/pzgsJ-HY">Custom Login</a> 2.0</li></ol><p><strong>For those looking to showoff your login screen, check out the <a\nhref="http://flickr.com/groups/custom-login/" rel="nofollow">Flickr group</a>! Share you designs with the community!</strong></p><p><iframe\nsrc="//extendd.com/?github-btn=true&#038;user=thefrosty&amp;repo=custom-login&amp;type=watch&amp;count=true&amp;size=large" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" scrolling="0" width="115" height="30"></iframe></p><h4>Hooks and Filters</h4><p>Full Documentation coming soon! For now visit the <a\nhref="http://wp.me/pzgsJ-HY">Custom Login</a> post on <a\nhref="http://austin.passy.co" title="Austin''s personal blog">austin.passy.co</a> for an overview of information and the action hooks to create a Custom Login Extension.</p><p><iframe\nid="youtube-white-label-2" type="text/html" class="autosize" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/XOZwaLwpjNo?&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;autohide=1&amp;controls=0&amp;hd=1&amp;rel=0&amp;border=0&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;fullscreen=1&amp;disablekb=1" style="border:0; height:360px; width:640px"></iframe><span\nclass="white-label" style="display:none;visability:hidden"><a\nhref="http://austinpassy.com/wordpress-plugins/youtube-white-label-shortcode" title="Powered by YouTube White Label Shortcode" rel="bookmark">White Label</a></span></p><p>The post <a\nrel="nofollow" href="https://extendd.com/plugin/custom-login/">Custom Login 2.0</a> appeared first on <a\nrel="nofollow" href="https://extendd.com">Extendd</a>.</p> ";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:45:"https://extendd.com/plugin/custom-login/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:9:"         ";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:6:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:24:"WP.com Image Feed Widget";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:52:"https://extendd.com/plugin/wp-com-image-feed-widget/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:61:"https://extendd.com/plugin/wp-com-image-feed-widget/#comments";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Thu, 21 Feb 2013 23:20:49 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17: