(97, 1, '2014-10-03 05:59:17', '2014-10-03 09:59:17', '[vc_row type="full_width_background" bg_position="center center" bg_repeat="no-repeat" scene_position="center" text_color="dark" text_align="center" top_padding="75" bottom_padding="50"][vc_column width="1/1"][heading]\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Manage Taxi Profiles</h1>\r\n[/heading][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row type="full_width_background" bg_position="left top" bg_repeat="no-repeat" bg_color="#ffffff" scene_position="center" text_color="dark" text_align="left" class="unregistered_user_information"][vc_column width="1/1" animation="none" column_padding="no-extra-padding" background_color_opacity="1" el_class="unregister_user_information"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">[icon color="Accent-Color" size="large-2" image="icon-th"]</h1>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Create and manage your taxi profiles for free. It helps you keep track of your day to day operation of each taxi, roster, expenses, and maintenance tasks. Managing a fleet of taxi is made simpler. Using our Taxi Profiles you can manage your fleet much more efficiently. It provides you a one-stop solution for maintaining the detailed book keeping, roster, payments, scheduled repairs, tolls etc.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">You can search history of your each taxi by each week at any time. So no more digging through the paper stack to find a specific info regarding a particular shift ever again! It also gives you a bigger picture by automatically calculating and showing how each individual taxis are performing. It also helps you concentrate more on your under performing taxi in your fleet.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row type="full_width_background" bg_position="left top" bg_repeat="no-repeat" scene_