(100, 1, '2014-10-03 12:14:06', '2014-10-03 16:14:06', '[vc_row type="full_width_background" bg_position="left top" bg_repeat="no-repeat" scene_position="center" text_color="dark" text_align="left" top_padding="45" bottom_padding="45" bg_color="#ffffff"][vc_column width="1/2"][divider line_type="No Line" custom_height="50"][vc_text_separator title="Services" title_align="separator_align_center"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Taxi Deals understands that being a professional driver and running a taxi business is stressful enough at its own right. We are here to help you by providing tailored automated services which requires less effort and time from your part so that, you can concentrate on your business easily.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Most of our services are offered either by our resident professionals or trusted partners fit to serve your taxi business. Our services are</strong></p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][divider line_type="No Line" custom_height="50"][divider line_type="No Line" custom_height="50"][vc_text_separator title="Accounting Services" title_align="separator_align_center"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">We provide our clients with an individually tailored range of accounting services and advice designed to satisfy statutory regulations, <strong>improve profitability</strong>, <strong>minimise tax liabilities</strong>, and <strong>maximise asset protection</strong>.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][divider line_type="No Line" custom_height="50"][divider line_type="No Line" custom_height="50"][vc_text_separator title="Tax / GST Lodge" title_align="separator_align_center"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Our taxation services are structured to ensure that you achieve the aim of <strong>paying no more tax than you need to</strong>. Taxi Deals has made GST lodge simple by making it automated.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][divider line_type="No Line" custom_height="50"][divider line_type="No Line" custom_height="50"][vc_text_separator title="Plate Lending / Finance" title_align="separator_align_center"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Our experience in taxi plate lending and finance manoeuvring can make all the difference in helping you <strong>reach your strategic goals</strong>.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][divider line_type="No Line" custom_height="50"][divider line_type="No Line" custom_height="50"][vc_text_separator title="Insurance" title_align="separator_align_center"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Our insurance experts can help you can make the informed decision. We also can help <strong>you get better rates</strong> through our accumulated buying power and industry knowledge.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][divider line_type="No Line" custom_height="50"][divider line_type="No Line" custom_height="50"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][divider line_type="No Line" custom_height="50"][divider line_type="No Line" custom_height="50"][image_with_animation image_url="479" alignment="center" animation="Fade In" img_link_target="_self"][divider line_type="No Line" custom_height="50"][vc_text_separator title="Legal Services" title_align="separator_align_center"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">We as taxi industry legal experts <strong>collaborate with drivers and operators</strong> at all stages to help them make the right choices and deliver efficient results.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][divider line_type="No Line" custom_height="50"][divider line_type="No Line" custom_height="50"][vc_text_separator title="Repair &amp; Maintenance" title_align="separator_align_center"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">We will help you make better decision that will maximise the operating life of your assets (taxi) and minimise your repair costs thus <strong>save your business money</strong> in the long run.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][divider line_type="No Line" custom_height="50"][divider line_type="No Line" custom_height="50"][vc_text_separator title="Taxi Towing" title_align="separator_align_center"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">We will list reliable contact details of towing truck drivers of different metropolitan areas who offer <strong>cheapest and fastest service</strong> under the given circumstances.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][divider line_type="No Line" custom_height="50"][divider line_type="No Line" custom_height="50"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row type="full_width_background" bg_position="left top" bg_repeat="no-repeat" bg_color="#ffffff" scene_position="center" text_color="dark" text_align="left"][vc_column width="1/1"][fancy-ul icon_type="standard_dash" icon="icon-glass" color="Accent-Color"][/fancy-ul][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row type="full_width_background" bg_position="left top" bg_repeat="no-repeat" bg_color="#ffffff" scene_position="center" text_color="dark" text_align="left"][vc_column width="1/1"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Service ', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'service', '', '', '2014-11-15 10:36:52', '2014-11-15 15:36:52', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/taxideals/?page_id=100', 0, 'page', '', 0),
