ty. If you have a specific business issue, or you are working on a large transaction, the effective management of your tax position is critical. Getting the right advice upfront can make a significant difference to the end result.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row type="full_width_background" bg_position="left top" bg_repeat="no-repeat" bg_color="#ffffff" scene_position="center" text_color="dark" text_align="left"][vc_column width="1/2" animation="none" column_padding="no-extra-padding" background_color="#ffffff" background_color_opacity="1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Tax Return for</strong></h4>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Individuals, Sole-traders,</li>\r\n	<li>Partnership, Trusts, Companies, &amp;</li>\r\n	<li>Self-managed super funds</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n[/vc_column_text][divider line_type="No Line" custom_height="20"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #333333;"><strong>Other Taxation Services</strong></span></h4>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Business set-ups and registrations</li>\r\n	<li>Tax planning and advisory services</li>\r\n	<li>Business Activity Statements (BAS)</li>\r\n	<li>Goods and Services Tax (GST)</li>\r\n	<li>Fringe Benefit Tax (FBT) &amp; Salary Sacrificing</li>\r\n	<li>Capital Gains Tax (CGT) including small business CGT concessions</li>\r\n	<li>Corporate and Secretarial Affairs</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n[/vc_column_text][divider line_type="No Line" custom_height="20"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Consulting Services</strong></h4>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Superannuation and Retirement Planning</li>\r\n	<li>Bookkeeping and other services based on client needs and expectations</li>\r\n	<li>Home, content, business, asset Insurance</li>\r\n	<li>Workers Compensation</li>\r\n	<li>Income Protection Insurance</li>\r\n	<li>Total Permanent Disablement (TDP)</li>\r\n	<li>Trauma and Life Insurance</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" animation="none" column_padding="no-extra-padding" background_color="#ffffff" background_color_opacity="1"][image_with_animation image_url="452" alignment="right" animation="Fade In" img_link_target="_self"][divider line_type="No Line" custom_height="50"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;">Simply give us a call or send us an email</h4>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">One of our experts will contact you shortly to discuss about your specific needs...</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row type="full_width_background" bg_position="left top" bg_repeat="no-repeat" bg_color="#ffffff" scene_position="center" text_color="dark" text_align="left"][vc_column width="1/1"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Accounting ', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'accounting', '', '', '2014-11-16 06:55:42', '2014-11-16 11:55:42', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/taxideals/?page_id=103', 0, 'page', '', 0),
