tify;">\r\n	<li>Less down-time for your taxis</li>\r\n	<li>Less repair and maintenance cost</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Taxi deals will provide further analysis of your maintenance history and can implement tailored maintenance plans and services for your fleet. We will help you make better decision that will maximise the operating life of your assets (taxi) and minimise your repair costs thus save your business money in the long run.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Repair & Maintenance', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'repair-maintenance', '', '', '2014-11-11 09:34:05', '2014-11-11 14:34:05', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/taxideals/?page_id=138', 0, 'page', '', 0),
