(281, 1, '2014-10-14 14:50:43', '2014-10-14 18:50:43', '[vc_row type="full_width_background" bg_position="center center" bg_repeat="no-repeat" scene_position="center" text_color="dark" text_align="center" top_padding="45" bottom_padding="45"][vc_column width="1/1" animation="none" centered_text="true" column_padding="no-extra-padding" background_color_opacity="1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">[icon color="Accent-Color" size="large-2" image="icon-book"]</p>\r\n\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Taxi School</h1>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>The Eligibility of becoming a taxi driver in NSW:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ol style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	<li>Be at least 20 years of age</li>\r\n	<li>Hold a current unrestricted/unconditional drivers license (minimum C) issued in New South Wales, and have held an unrestricted drivers license issued in any Australian state or territory for at least 12 months of the previous 2 years (L, P Plate &amp; Good Behaviour licenses are not accepted)</li>\r\n	<li>Be an Australian or New Zealand Citizen, permanent resident or hold a visa allowing you to work in Australia. (Student visas OK with work restrictions)</li>\r\n	<li>Pass the AMES NMES Taxi driver communication skills English assessment</li>\r\n	<li>Pass a health check with a medical practitioner - your GP</li>\r\n	<li>Clearance from the regulator, Transport for NSW.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">The Roads and Maritime Services and NSW Taxi Industry require any aspiring taxi driver to complete an accredited course, the Taxicare Plus – ‘Statement of Attainment in Taxi Driver Training Bronze Level’ for initial entry into the Taxi industry from a licensed training provider.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Once you have passed the tests from your training institution you will be booked to sit for a test at the Taxi authority office in Parramatta, Sydney.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Associated costs of getting a NSW taxi license:</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">These costs are given as an indication and may vary.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Training Fees</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ol style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	<li>Taxicare Bronze level training Fee – $700-$900 (The training fee and quality may vary from school to school)</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>External Fees</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ol style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	<li style="text-align: left;">English assessment at NSW AMES (Adult Migrant English Service)              Fee – $165</li>\r\n	<li style="text-align: left;">Medical assessment Fee – See your own Doctor                                               Fee – $50</li>\r\n	<li style="text-align: left;">4 Taxi Size Pictures (65x65mm)                                                                             Fee – $30</li>\r\n	<li style="text-align: left;">Transport NSW Min Taxi Authority processing fee (valid 6 months)             Fee – $100</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">There are a number of taxi schools or training providers in Sydney. The following are the most reputed taxi training schools and run frequent courses.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Punchbowl </strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Phone: (02) 9649 7447 Mobile: Andrew Nicholas: 0411 092 348 Email: info@thesydneytaxischool.com Address: Suite 2, Level 1, 200 The Boulevard, (PO Box 345) Punchbowl, 2196.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Opening Hours:</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Weekdays (Monday-Thursday)             9:00am-9:00pm (Closed Public Holidays)</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Weekends (Friday-Saturday)                 9:00am-4:00pm</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Taxi Schools', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '152-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-10-14 14:50:43', '2014-10-14 18:50:43', '', 152, 'http://localhost:8080/taxideals/152-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
