(225, 1, '2014-10-11 07:30:34', '2014-10-11 11:30:34', '[vc_row type="full_width_background" bg_position="center center" bg_repeat="no-repeat" scene_position="center" text_color="dark" text_align="center" top_padding="45" bottom_padding="45"][vc_column width="1/1" animation="none" centered_text="true" column_padding="no-extra-padding" background_color_opacity="1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">[icon color="Accent-Color" size="large-2" image="icon-usd"]</h1>\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Tax/GST Lodge</h1>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">As a professional driver you need to lodge your GST that you have collected from the passengers. Taxi Deals has made GST lodge very easy. Simply fill in the ‘GST lodge form’ and send it to us. We will have it checked by professional accountants and lodge it for you.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Our taxation services are structured to ensure that you achieve the aim of paying no more tax than you need to, and to provide support services to assist with your tax/GST returns, calculations and payments.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Drivers need to fill in the ‘blank GST return form’ and send it to us so that we can process your GST lodgment. Also see the ‘example GST form’ (filled out) if you are unsure how to complete the form correctly.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Tax / GST Lodge', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '106-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-10-11 07:30:34', '2014-10-11 11:30:34', '', 106, 'http://localhost:8080/taxideals/106-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
