x (CGT) including small business CGT concessions</li>\r\n	<li>Corporate and Secretarial Affairs</li>\r\n	<li>Superannuation and Retirement Planning</li>\r\n	<li>Bookkeeping Services</li>\r\n	<li>And others based on client needs and expectations</li>\r\n	<li>Home and content Insurance</li>\r\n	<li>Business Insurances</li>\r\n	<li>Workers Compensation</li>\r\n	<li>Income Protection Insurance</li>\r\n	<li>Total Permanent Disablement (TDP)</li>\r\n	<li>Trauma and</li>\r\n	<li>Life Insurance</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Accounting ', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '103-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-10-11 07:35:20', '2014-10-11 11:35:20', '', 103, 'http://localhost:8080/taxideals/103-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(229, 1, '2014-10-11 07:37:57', '2014-10-11 11:37:57', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Service</h1>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Taxi Deals understands that being a professional driver and running a taxi business is stressful enough at its own right. We are here to help you by providing tailored automated services which requires less effort and time from your part so that, you can concentrate on your business easily.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Most of our services are offered either by our resident professionals or trusted partners fit to serve your taxi business. Our services are,</p>\r\n\r\n<ol style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	<li><strong>Accounting Services</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">We provide our clients with an individually tailored range of accounting services and advice designed to satisfy statutory regulations, improve profitability, minimise tax liabilities, and maximise asset protection.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong> </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ol style="text-align: justify;" start="2">\r\n	<li><strong>Tax/GST Lodge</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Our taxation services are structured to ensure that you achieve the aim of paying no more tax than you need to. Taxi Deals has made GST lodge simple by making it automated.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong> </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ol style="text-align: justify;" start="3">\r\n	<li><strong>Plate Lending/Finance Services:</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Our experience in taxi plate lending and finance maneuvering can make all the difference in helping you reach your strategic goals.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong> </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ol style="text-align: justify;" start="4">\r\n	<li><strong>Insurance </strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Our insurance experts can help you can make the informed decision. We also can help you get better rates through our accumulated buying power and industry knowledge.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong> </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ol style="text-align: justify;" start="5">\r\n	<li><strong>Legal Services</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">We as taxi industry legal experts collaborate with drivers and operators at all stages to help them make the right choices and deliver efficient results.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong> </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ol style="text-align: justify;" start="6">\r\n	<li><strong>Repair and maintenance</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">We will help you make better decision that will maximise the operating life of your assets (taxi) and minimise your repair costs thus save your business money in the long run.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol style="text-align: justify;" start="7">\r\n	<li><strong>Taxi Towing</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">We will list reliable contact details of towing truck drivers of different metropolitan areas who offer cheapest and fastest service under the given circumstances.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Service ', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '100-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-10-11 07:37:57', '2014-10-11 11:37:57', '', 100, 'http://localhost:8080/taxideals/100-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(230, 1, '2014-10-11 07:39:08', '2014-10-11 11:39:08', '[vc_row type="in_container" bg_position="left top" bg_repeat="no-repeat" scene_position="center" text_color="dark" text_align="left" top_padding="45" bottom_padding="45"][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Service</h1>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Taxi Deals understands that being a professional driver and running a taxi business is stressful enough at its own right. We are here to help you by providing tailored automated services which requires less effort and time from your part so that, you can concentrate on your business easily.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Most of our services are offered either by our resident professionals or trusted partners fit to serve your taxi business. Our services are,</p>\r\n\r\n<ol style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	<li><strong>Accounting Services</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">We provide our clients with an individually tailored range of accounting services and advice designed to satisfy statutory regulations, improve profitability, minimise tax liabilities, and maximise asset protection.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong> </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ol style="text-align: justify;" start="2">\r\n	<li><strong>Tax/GST Lodge</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Our taxation services are structured to ensure that you achieve the aim of paying no more tax than you need to. Taxi Deals has made GST lodge simple by making it automated.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong> </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ol style="text-align: justify;" start="3">\r\n	<li><strong>Plate Lending/Finance Services:</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Our experience in taxi plate lending and finance maneuvering can make all the difference in helping you reach your strategic goals.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong> </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ol style="text-align: justify;" start="4">\r\n	<li><strong>Insurance </strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Our insurance experts can help you can make the informed decision. We also can help you get better rates through our accumulated buying power and industry knowledge.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong> </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ol style="text-align: justify;" start="5">\r\n	<li><strong>Legal Services</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">We as taxi industry legal experts collaborate with drivers and operators at all stages to help them make the right choices and deliver efficient results.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong> </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ol style="text-align: justify;" start="6">\r\n	<li><strong>Repair and maintenance</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">We will help you make better decision that will maximise the operating life of your assets (taxi) and minimise your repair costs thus save your business money in the long run.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol style="text-align: justify;" start="7">\r\n	<li><strong>Taxi Towing</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">We will list reliable contact details of towing truck drivers of different metropolitan areas who offer cheapest and fastest service under the given circumstances.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Service ', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '100-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-10-11 07:39:08', '2014-10-11 11:39:08', '', 100, 'http://localhost:8080/taxideals/100-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
