(336, 1, '2014-10-17 15:49:42', '2014-10-17 19:49:42', '[vc_row type="full_width_background" bg_position="center center" bg_repeat="no-repeat" scene_position="center" text_color="dark" text_align="center" top_padding="75" bottom_padding="50"][vc_column width="1/1" animation="none" centered_text="true" column_padding="no-extra-padding" background_color_opacity="1"][heading]\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Accounting</h1>\r\n[/heading][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row type="full_width_background" bg_position="left top" bg_repeat="no-repeat" scene_position="center" text_color="dark" text_align="left" top_padding="0" bottom_padding="75"][vc_column width="1/1" animation="none" column_padding="no-extra-padding" background_color_opacity="1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">[icon color="Accent-Color" size="large-2" image="icon-usd"]</h1>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">We provide our clients with an individually tailored range of accounting services and advice designed to satisfy statutory regulations, improve profitability, minimise tax liabilities, and maximise asset protection. When appropriate we can also recommend and co-ordinate other services offered by Taxi Deals accountancy &amp; advisory services, providing our clients with access to a wealth of resources for all of their financial needs.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">An increasing focus on regulation and governance, the fast pace of legislative change and potentially severe penalties for non-compliance, means that navigating tax issues can be challenging - but with every challenge comes opportunity. If you have a specific business issue, or you are working on a large transaction, the effective management of your tax position is critical. Getting the right advice upfront can make a significant difference to the end result.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n<h4>Tax Return for:</h4>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Individuals Sole-traders, Partnership, Trusts, Companies, &amp; Self-managed s