(455, 1, '2014-10-30 10:30:32', '2014-10-30 14:30:32', '[vc_row type="full_width_background" bg_position="center center" bg_repeat="no-repeat" scene_position="center" text_color="dark" text_align="center" top_padding="75" bottom_padding="50"][vc_column width="1/1" animation="none" centered_text="true" column_padding="no-extra-padding" background_color_opacity="1"][heading]\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Plate Lending &amp; Finance</h1>\r\n[/heading][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row type="full_width_background" bg_position="center center" bg_repeat="no-repeat" scene_position="center" text_color="dark" text_align="center" top_padding="0" bottom_padding="5"][vc_column width="1/1" animation="none" centered_text="true" column_padding="no-extra-padding" background_color_opacity="1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">[icon color="Accent-Color" image="icon-key"]</h1>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row type="in_container" bg_position="left top" bg_repeat="no-repeat" scene_position="center" text_color="dark" text_align="left" bottom_padding="75"][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">We provide our clients with an individually tailored range of accounting services and advice designed to satisfy statutory regulations, improve profitability, minimise tax liabilities, and maximise asset protection. When appropriate we can also recommend and co-ordinate other services offered by Taxi Deal’s resident accountancy &amp; advisory services, providing our clients with access to a wealth of resources for all of their financial needs.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Our experience in finance maneuvering can make all the difference in helping you reach your strategic goals.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify;">Car Loans</li>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify;">Plate &amp; Equipment Loans</li>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify;">Commercial Loans</li>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justif