(474, 1, '2014-10-30 23:56:19', '2014-10-31 03:56:19', '[vc_row type="full_width_background" bg_position="center center" bg_repeat="no-repeat" scene_position="center" text_color="dark" text_align="center" top_padding="75" bottom_padding="50"][vc_column width="1/1"][heading]\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Tax / GST Lodge</h1>\r\n[/heading][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row type="full_width_background" bg_position="center center" bg_repeat="no-repeat" scene_position="center" text_color="dark" text_align="center" top_padding="0" bottom_padding="5"][vc_column width="1/1" animation="none" centered_text="true" column_padding="no-extra-padding" background_color_opacity="1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">[icon color="Accent-Color" size="large-2" image="icon-usd"]</h1>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row type="full_width_background" bg_position="center center" bg_repeat="no-repeat" scene_position="center" text_color="dark" text_align="center" top_padding="0" bottom_padding="75"][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>GST Lodge for Professional Drivers</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">As a professional driver you need to lodge your GST quarterly that you have collected from the passengers. Taxi Deals has made GST lodge very easy. Simply fill in the ‘GST lodge form’ and send it to us. We will have it checked by professional tax agents and lodge it for you.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][divider line_type="No Line" custom_height="50"][image_with_animation image_url="462" animation="Fade In" img_link_target="_self"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>How Taxi Deals can help</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Our taxation services are structured to ensure that you achieve the aim of paying no more tax than you need to, and to provide support services to assist with your tax/GST returns, calculations and payments.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>How this works</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Drivers need to fill in the ‘blank GST return form’ and send it to us so that we can process your GST lodgment on your behalf. Also see the ‘example GST form’ (filled out) if you are unsure how to complete the form correctly.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][divider line_type="No Line" custom_height="50"][image_with_animation image_url="463" animation="Fade In" img_link_target="_self"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Tax / GST Lodge', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '106-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-10-30 23:56:19', '2014-10-31 03:56:19', '', 106, 'http://localhost:8080/taxideals/106-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
