(723, 10, '2014-11-11 09:32:49', '2014-11-11 14:32:49', '[vc_row type="full_width_background" bg_position="center center" bg_repeat="no-repeat" scene_position="center" text_color="dark" text_align="center" top_padding="48" bottom_padding="15" bg_color="#ffffff"][vc_column width="1/1" animation="none" centered_text="true" column_padding="no-extra-padding" background_color_opacity="1"][vc_column_text]\n\nI am text block. Click edit button to change this text.\n\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row type="in_container" bg_position="left top" bg_repeat="no-repeat" scene_position="center" text_color="dark" text_align="left" bottom_padding="75"][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Taxi Deals can assist you with your with fleet of taxis to minimise your repair and maintenance cost by implementing Asset Management and Preventative Maintenance principles. Taxi Deals has developed a taxi maintenance regime (software) which will help you efficiently manage the repair and maintenance of your taxi fleet. Simply start using the “Maintenance History Form” listed in the operators’ dashboard area and the benefits will become apparent to you in no time!</p>\n\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;"><strong>The features of our taxi maintenance regime</strong></h4>\n<ul style="text-align: justify;">\n	<li style="text-align: left;">Keep track of your maintenance history</li>\n	<li style="text-align: left;">You can schedule your next repairs</li>\n	<li style="text-align: left;">List inventory of required repair parts</li>\n	<li style="text-align: left;">Automated data analysis for crucial decision making</li>\n</ul>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;"><strong>The benefits are simple. You can save by having</strong></h4>\n<ul style="text-align: justify;">\n	<li>Less down-time for your taxis</li>\n	<li>Less repair and maintenance cost</li>\n</ul>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Taxi deals will provide further analysis of your maintenance history and can implement tailored maintenance plans and services for your fleet. We will help you make better decision that will maximise the operating life of your assets (taxi) and minimise your repair costs thus save your business money in the long run.</p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Repair & Maintenance', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '138-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-11-11 09:32:49', '2014-11-11 14:32:49', '', 138, 'http://localhost:8080/taxideals/138-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
