(742, 10, '2014-11-11 10:31:14', '2014-11-11 15:31:14', '[vc_row type="full_width_background" bg_position="center center" bg_repeat="no-repeat" scene_position="center" text_color="dark" text_align="center" top_padding="48" bottom_padding="15" bg_color="#ffffff"][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\n\nI am text block. Click edit button to change this text.\n\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row type="full_width_background" bg_position="left top" bg_repeat="no-repeat" scene_position="center" text_color="dark" text_align="left" top_padding="0" bottom_padding="75"][vc_column width="1/2" animation="none" centered_text="true" column_padding="no-extra-padding" background_color_opacity="1"][vc_text_separator title="Taxi Industry Challenges" title_align="separator_align_center"][vc_column_text]\n<p style="text-align: center;">In Australia, the challenges of Taxi industry are volatile finance costs, fuel prices, tighter regulations, and increased competition. Those operating within the Australian Taxi market must also address growing environmental concerns and satisfy consumer demand for cleaner, greener cars. However, such challenges have encouraged new investment and innovation, as well as increased government assistance to the Australian Taxi industry today.</p>\n\n<h4 style="text-align: center;"><strong>We as market experts collaborate with drivers and operators at all stages to help them make the right choices and deliver efficient results.</strong></h4>\n[/vc_column_text][divider line_type="No Line" custom_height="50"][image_with_animation image_url="464" animation="Fade In" img_link_target="_self"][divider line_type="No Line" custom_height="50"][vc_column_text]\n<h4 style="text-align: center;">Taxi Deals Legal Team</h4>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Taxi Deals legal practice professionals can help turn your business issues into opportunities. We offer a range of services in areas impacting Taxi businesses, including legal, customs, transfer pricing, and general legal advisory services.</p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\n<h4 style="text-align: center;"><strong>We encourage you to make use of the resources we offer on our website and to engage us in discussion on how we can leverage our capabilities to address your business needs and challenges.</strong></h4>\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;"></h4>\n[/vc_column_text][image_with_animation image_url="457" animation="Fade In" img_link_target="_self"][divider line_type="No Line" custom_height="50"][vc_column_text]\n<h4 style="text-align: center;">How Taxi Deals can help you?</h4>\n<p style="text-align: center;">To address these business challenges, Taxi Deals offers a strong and reliable network of dedicated industry experts. Taxi businesses choose to work with a professional services organisation that has its finger on the pulse of the Taxi industry; an organisation that deeply understands the industry''s fundamental issues and brings the experience to provide solutions that work.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Taxi Deals Australia''s dedicated Taxi practice</strong>, with its local industry experience as well as links to the global network, offers the highest level of expertise to add value to your operations.</p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Legal Services', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '125-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-11-11 10:31:14', '2014-11-11 15:31:14', '', 125, 'http://localhost:8080/taxideals/125-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
