(827, 10, '2014-11-16 06:51:53', '2014-11-16 11:51:53', '[vc_row type="full_width_background" bg_position="center center" bg_repeat="no-repeat" scene_position="center" text_color="dark" text_align="center" top_padding="48" bottom_padding="15" bg_color="#ffffff"][vc_column width="1/1" animation="none" centered_text="true" column_padding="no-extra-padding" background_color_opacity="1"][vc_column_text]\n<h1 style="text-align: left;">[icon color="Accent-Color" size="normal" image="icon-usd"] Accounting Services</h1>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row type="full_width_background" bg_position="left top" bg_repeat="no-repeat" scene_position="center" text_color="dark" text_align="left" top_padding="35" bottom_padding="25" bg_color="#ffffff"][vc_column width="1/2" animation="none" column_padding="no-extra-padding" background_color_opacity="1"][vc_column_text]\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Taxi Industry Focused Services</strong></p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">We provide our clients with an individually tailored range of accounting services and advice designed to satisfy statutory regulations, improve profitability, minimise tax liabilities, and maximise asset protection. When appropriate we can also recommend and co-ordinate other services offered by Taxi Deals accountancy &amp; advisory services, providing our clients with access to a wealth of resources for all of their financial needs.</p>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]\n\n&nbsp;\n\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_text_separator title="Legislative Challenges" title_align="separator_align_center"][vc_column_text]\n<p style="text-align: justify;">An increasing focus on regulation and governance, the fast pace of legislative change and potentially severe penalties for non-compliance, means that navigating tax issues can be challenging - but with every challenge comes opportunity. If you have a specific business issue, or you are working on a large transaction, the effective management of your tax position is critical. Getting the right advice upfront can make a significant difference to the end result.</p>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]\n\n&nbsp;\n\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row type="full_width_background" bg_position="left top" bg_repeat="no-repeat" bg_color="#ffffff" scene_position="center" text_color="dark" text_align="left"][vc_column width="1/2" animation="none" column_padding="no-extra-padding" background_color="#ffffff" background_color_opacity="1"][vc_column_text]\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Tax Return for</strong></h4>\n<ol>\n	<li>Individuals, Sole-traders,</li>\n	<li>Partnership, Trusts, Companies, &amp;</li>\n	<li>Self-managed super funds</li>\n</ol>\n[/vc_column_text][divider line_type="No Line" custom_height="20"][vc_column_text]\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #333333;"><strong>Other Taxation Services</strong></span></h4>\n<ol>\n	<li>Business set-ups and registrations</li>\n	<li>Tax planning and advisory services</li>\n	<li>Business Activity Statements (BAS)</li>\n	<li>Goods and Services Tax (GST)</li>\n	<li>Fringe Benefit Tax (FBT) &amp; Salary Sacrificing</li>\n	<li>Capital Gains Tax (CGT) including small business CGT concessions</li>\n	<li>Corporate and Secretarial Affairs</li>\n</ol>\n[/vc_column_text][divider line_type="No Line" custom_height="20"][vc_column_text]\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Consulting Services</strong></h4>\n<ol>\n	<li>Superannuation and Retirement Planning</li>\n	<li>Bookkeeping and other services based on client needs and expectations</li>\n	<li>Home, content, business, asset Insurance</li>\n	<li>Workers Compensation</li>\n	<li>Income Protection Insurance</li>\n	<li>Total Permanent Disablement (TDP)</li>\n	<li>Trauma and Life Insurance</li>\n</ol>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]\n\n&nbsp;\n\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" animation="none" column_padding="no-extra-padding" background_color="#ffffff" background_color_opacity="1"][image_with_animation image_url="452" alignment="right" animation="Fade In" img_link_target="_self"][divider line_type="No Line" custom_height="50"][vc_column_text]\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;">Simply give us a call or send us an email</h4>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">One of our experts will contact you shortly to discuss about your specific needs...</p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Accounting ', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '103-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-11-16 06:51:53', '2014-11-16 11:51:53', '', 103, 'http://localhost:8080/taxideals/103-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
